Package navmid.parser Description

This package implements the parsing of result file from navstatic (previous version used Matos). These are XML files where we can identify three parts:

  • identification of abstract nodes representing live objects allocated in a given context.
  • relations established between abstract nodes. This analysis is the result of a points-to analysis on identified methods
  • callback analysis where control flow is locally explored.
